---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Elote King — Case Study | Hayaan Dangra"
  description="How I built a website, ran SEO, and sold out 2 events for my family's food business."
>
  <section class="hero section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="tag">Case Study</span>
        <h1>Elote King: From Idea to Sold-Out Events</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          How I used web development and SEO to help launch my family's food business.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="challenge section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The Challenge</h2>
      <div class="content">
        <p>
          My family wanted to launch Elote King — a food business selling Mexican street corn. We had great food but no online presence, no way to reach customers, and no proof that people would actually show up to events.
        </p>
        <p class="highlight">
          The question: Could I build something online that would actually get people to show up in person?
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="built section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What I Built</h2>
      <div class="built-grid">
        <div class="built-item">
          <div class="number">1</div>
          <h3>Landing Page</h3>
          <p>
            Built a clean, conversion-focused site with event info, menu showcase, and email signup. Used Astro for speed and Formspree for the signup form.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="built-item">
          <div class="number">2</div>
          <h3>SEO Strategy</h3>
          <p>
            Targeted local keywords like "elote near me" and "Mexican street corn [city]". Optimized meta tags, structured data, and Google Business Profile.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="built-item">
          <div class="number">3</div>
          <h3>Email List</h3>
          <p>
            Created a signup funnel that captured 300+ emails before our first event. Each subscriber got event reminders and location updates.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="built-item">
          <div class="number">4</div>
          <h3>Social Proof Loop</h3>
          <p>
            Posted in local Facebook groups, added QR codes to flyers, and let the signups speak for themselves.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="results section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The Results</h2>
      <div class="results-grid">
        <div class="result-card">
          <div class="result-number">300+</div>
          <div class="result-label">Email Signups</div>
          <div class="result-detail">Before first event</div>
        </div>
        <div class="result-card">
          <div class="result-number">2</div>
          <div class="result-label">Sold-Out Events</div>
          <div class="result-detail">Back-to-back</div>
        </div>
        <div class="result-card">
          <div class="result-number">✓</div>
          <div class="result-label">Business Validated</div>
          <div class="result-detail">Family invested in trailer</div>
        </div>
        <div class="result-card">
          <div class="result-number">∞</div>
          <div class="result-label">Permanent Hub</div>
          <div class="result-detail">Website still running</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="learnings section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What I Learned</h2>
      <div class="content">
        <ul class="learnings-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Validate before you invest.</strong> The website proved demand before we spent thousands on a food trailer.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Simple landing pages convert better than complex sites.</strong> I removed everything that wasn't pushing toward the signup form.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Local SEO works fast when you target specific queries.</strong> We ranked for "elote near me" within weeks.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>The code doesn't matter if the offer isn't clear.</strong> I rewrote the hero copy 4 times before signups took off.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <p>Want to see what else I've built?</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/math-explorations" class="button">Math Explorations</a>
          <a href="/" class="button-secondary">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange) 0%, #D35400 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }
  }

  .challenge,
  .learnings {
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .built {
    background-color: var(--light-gray);
  }

  .results {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--white) 0%, var(--light-gray) 100%);
  }

  .cta {
    background-color: var(--light-gray);
  }

  h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .content p {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }
  }

  .highlight {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .highlight {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }

  .built-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .built-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .built-item {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    position: relative;
  }

  .number {
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--space-lg);
    right: var(--space-lg);
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background-color: var(--orange);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .built-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }

  .built-item p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }

  .results-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 480px) {
    .results-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .results-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .result-card {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-top: 4px solid var(--orange);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .result-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .result-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--orange);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .result-label {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .result-detail {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #7f8c8d;
  }

  .learnings-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .learnings-list li {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding-left: var(--space-xl);
    position: relative;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .learnings-list li {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }

  .learnings-list li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .learnings-list strong {
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cta-content p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .button-secondary {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg);
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--blue);
    border: 2px solid var(--blue);
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .button-secondary:hover {
    background-color: var(--blue);
    color: var(--white);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
